General.Name: CryCash
General.Description:
CryCash is a gaming platform that aims to disrupt the gaming industry by creating marketing tools for game developers based on the Ethereum blockchain, and give gamers the possibility to receive tokens by completing tasks set by game developers. The platform will feature the Plink application, an advertising platform, a decentralized marketplace and cybersport tournaments. The Plink app will be used asÂ the payment method within the platform, and to store CryCash tokens, just to new a few.

CryCash token (CRC) is an ERC-20 token that will work as the medium of exchange within the platform.
